  • public class FishFood
extends AquariumObject
    Class itb.akadquarium.FishFood. This class is derived from itb.akadquarium.AquariumObject. It is used as the food of itb.akadquarium.Guppy - a derived itb.akadquarium.Fish object. itb.akadquarium.FishFood is bought by the player using the coin while the game is running.
